  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\n<div class=\"ab-player\"><div class=\"ab-video\"><video controls=\"\" preload=\"metadata\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/pw3zwq.MP4\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></video> </div></div><br/>\r\n网传涿州救援发现浮尸（未经求证）<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYjAwMDFkYzdhMTRiYmJmZTZmNThlLmpwZz93aWR0aD04MzEmaGVpZ2h0PTEyODA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b0001dc7a14bbbfe6f58e.jpg?width=831&amp;height=1280\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b0001dc7a14bbbfe6f58e.jpg?width=831&amp;height=1280\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b0001dc7a14bbbfe6f58e.jpg?width=831&amp;height=1280\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a>、                                <b>   河北省行政区域地图</b><br/>\r\n      <br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\r\n    <a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYWUyYWY2NDRhZDkxYjRmMmNlYTdkLmpwZz93aWR0aD04MDAmaGVpZ2h0PTM0MA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ae2af644ad91b4f2cea7d.jpg?width=800&amp;height=340\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ae2af644ad91b4f2cea7d.jpg?width=800&amp;height=340\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ae2af644ad91b4f2cea7d.jpg?width=800&amp;height=340\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n                <b>    雄安新区在河北省的位置</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZmVjNDRjZjZmY2FkYjI0OGZhMDAzLmpwZz93aWR0aD04MDAmaGVpZ2h0PTk5MA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/fec44cf6fcadb248fa003.jpg?width=800&amp;height=990\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/fec44cf6fcadb248fa003.jpg?width=800&amp;height=990\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/fec44cf6fcadb248fa003.jpg?width=800&amp;height=990\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n             <b>  海河流域图小圈大致涿州位置，大圈大致雄安新区位置</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<b><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvY2Y1N2IwZDgxY2VmYTJkMTI5ZGY5LnBuZz93aWR0aD05NTEmaGVpZ2h0PTE1NTU\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/cf57b0d81cefa2d129df9.png?width=951&amp;height=1555\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/cf57b0d81cefa2d129df9.png?width=951&amp;height=1555\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/cf57b0d81cefa2d129df9.png?width=951&amp;height=1555\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a></b><br/>\n<br/>\n<b>海河流域示意图。图源：中国国家地理  </b><br/>\n<br/>\n<b><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9wb21mMi5sYWluLmxhL2YvZ2c4eG9nZ3UuanBnP3dpZHRoPTI0ODAmaGVpZ2h0PTI5ODI\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://pomf2.lain.la/f/gg8xoggu.jpg?width=2480&amp;height=2982\"><img alt=\"https://pomf2.lain.la/f/gg8xoggu.jpg?width=2480&amp;height=2982\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://pomf2.lain.la/f/gg8xoggu.jpg?width=2480&amp;height=2982\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a></b><br/>\n<br/>\r\n                                       <b>        7处蓄滞洪区位置示意图。 图片来源于人民网</b><br/>\n<br/>\r\n    <br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMGJiZTQ0MDg5YzcxNzAyYTQzZWFmLmpwZz93aWR0aD03MTYmaGVpZ2h0PTQ4OA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0bbe44089c71702a43eaf.jpg?width=716&amp;height=488\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0bbe44089c71702a43eaf.jpg?width=716&amp;height=488\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0bbe44089c71702a43eaf.jpg?width=716&amp;height=488\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n                <b> 重点区域海拔图</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<b><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMTBlODY3MzRkNzY2M2JhMzViMmFkLmpwZz93aWR0aD0zMTAmaGVpZ2h0PTIxMQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/10e86734d7663ba35b2ad.jpg?width=310&amp;height=211\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/10e86734d7663ba35b2ad.jpg?width=310&amp;height=211\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/10e86734d7663ba35b2ad.jpg?width=310&amp;height=211\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a></b><br/>\r\n      <b> 海河流域蓄滞洪区“白洋淀”位于雄安新区核心位置</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<b><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYjRiY2QzNWNjODExMzBiNmQzNDU0LmpwZz93aWR0aD00NjgmaGVpZ2h0PTIwOQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b4bcd35cc81130b6d3454.jpg?width=468&amp;height=209\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b4bcd35cc81130b6d3454.jpg?width=468&amp;height=209\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b4bcd35cc81130b6d3454.jpg?width=468&amp;height=209\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a></b><br/>\n<b> 水利部：确保雄安新区安全</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<b><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNjA0MmFmNjI2MDAwMGZmOGIzMGU3LnBuZz93aWR0aD00ODEmaGVpZ2h0PTgzNA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/6042af6260000ff8b30e7.png?width=481&amp;height=834\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/6042af6260000ff8b30e7.png?width=481&amp;height=834\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/6042af6260000ff8b30e7.png?width=481&amp;height=834\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a></b><br/>\n<br/>\n<b>   闽江新军其中一员倪岳峰：坚决当好首都“护城河”</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<b>目前观点：</b><br/>\n<b>一：确认人为泄洪，上保北京，下保雄安</b><br/>\n<b>二：政府职能失序，权力真空。(武警力量可能4号才进入，多靠民间自救)</b><br/>\n<b>三：人员伤亡不大，如有也是个例。(如有大规模伤亡，不可能一张照片都没出来，后期已经开始         救猫救狗了)</b><br/>\n<b>四：舆论导向依旧是按照管理没有升级（一如既往的甩锅，归咎，感动。）</b><br/>\n<b>五：后期就是关于财产损失定损和赔偿比例的问题</b><br/>\n<b>六：霸州县政府维权矛盾点在于官方降雨和民间泄洪，关于定责事后赔偿的问题。</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<b>8.5日更新：霸州“官方降雨”“民间泄洪”观点冲突，群众聚集政府大楼讨要说法<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9wb21mMi5sYWluLmxhL2YvNWRyaXg5enAuanBnP3dpZHRoPTExNzkmaGVpZ2h0PTEwMjc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://pomf2.lain.la/f/5drix9zp.jpg?width=1179&amp;height=1027\"><img alt=\"https://pomf2.lain.la/f/5drix9